## 7. Cross-product integration touchpoints

Every entry below uses one of the three patterns from §4.

| Touchpoint | Pattern | Direction |
|---|---|---|
| Financials reads project master, parties, CBS | A — Synchronous lookup | Financials → CIMS |
| Financials reads RFIs and drawing references | A — Synchronous lookup | Financials → CIMS |
| Financials publishes change events | B — Event publication | Financials → CIMS → (QA, Optimisation) |
| Financials publishes payment certificates | C — Document handoff | Financials → CIMS |
| Financials publishes final accounts | C — Document handoff | Financials → CIMS |
| Financials subscribes to ITP completion events | B — Event subscription | QA → CIMS → Financials |
| Financials subscribes to schedule progress events | B — Event subscription | Optimisation → CIMS → Financials |
| Financials publishes budget and actuals to optimisation | B — Event publication | Financials → CIMS → Optimisation |

