## 10. Out of scope of this plan

These are deliberate exclusions. Each will be re-evaluated only when triggered by a separate decision.

- **Revit one-click cascade.** A separate future application that consumes the four products' APIs in the same hub-and-spoke pattern. Treated as a fifth product, not a feature of any of the four.
- **Native BIM viewer or model coordination.** Embedded via Speckle, Autodesk APS, xeokit / web-ifc, or BCF only. Building this in-house is a multi-year specialist engineering effort that would consume the entire roadmap.
- **Replacing the customer's general ledger.** F8 integrates with Xero, Sage, QuickBooks; the GL stays where the customer's accounting team already runs it.
- **Mobile field app with full offline capability.** A scoped PWA for snagging and permits-to-work capture is on the post-MVP backlog. Full mobile parity is not.
- **Resource management, equipment management, T&M.** Out of scope for v1; potential post-Phase 2.

